Template: ibus-easy-config/install-ibus-globally
Type: select
Default: Yes
Choices: Yes, No, Not Sure
Description: Do You Want To Install IBus Globally?
 If you choose "Yes" (or "Not Sure"), I will install IBus globally and for all the users logged in.
 .
 If you are not sure what to do, it is safe to select Yes.

Template: ibus-easy-config/start-now
Type: select
Default: Yes
Choices: Yes, No
Description: Start IBus Easy Config Now?
 Do you want to start IBus Easy Config now? You can select your language and start typing easily.
 You can also customize your shortcut easily.
 .
 If you are not sure what to do, it is safe to select Yes.

Template: ibus-easy-config/select-user
Type: select
Choices: ${choices}
Description: Who Are You?
 It seems that more than one user is currently logged in. I am stupid and can't detect who you are :-(.
 Please select your name from the list.
 .
 P.S.: Please select the correct user or the installation will not be ok. You can find your user name usually on the upper right corner.
